name: UFW Firewall
description: Uncomplicated Firewall - simple firewall configuration tool
version: 1.0
author: Alfred System
category: security

Features:
  - Enable basic firewall
  - Allow SSH connections
  - Deny all other incoming traffic
  - Simple management interface

Notes:
  - Requires root privileges
  - Will block all incoming traffic except SSH
  - Default outgoing traffic is allowed